description: Set on over half an acre in Beverly Hills, this exceptional 6-bd, 6-ba estate offers nearly 6,000 sq ft of thoughtfully designed living space, masterfully crafted for luxury, comfort, and style. Surrounded by lush nature, this newly built home is just moments from the scenic trails of Franklin Canyon Park, the family-friendly playgrounds of Coldwater Park, and only minutes from the world-renowned shopping and dining of Rodeo Drive. Step inside to discover a truly one-of-a-kind design with every detail expertly curated to blend timeless elegance with modern sophistication. Expansive living areas, oversized bedrooms, refined finishes, and a seamless indoor-outdoor flow create an ideal setting for both relaxed living and stylish entertaining. Private, elegant, and perfectly located this is one of Beverly Hills' finest homes. A rare opportunity not to be missed.
